[h4 id=RollingHp 
	"Rolling HP
	$LF
]h4
[div class=p 
	"Another thing to introduce is the rolling HP mechanic, returning from Earthbound/Mother 2. When you take damage, your health rolls down. The quirk of this is that if you take a lethal hit, you donâ€™t actually die until your health rolls to 0, and if you can heal in time, you will survive. Another quirk is that if you win the battle before losing all damage inflicted, it wonâ€™t be dealt to you. The last quirk is that defending will slow the rolling, buying time at the cost of an action. This will come in handy at times in the TAS. 
	$LF
]div
